file.name: fpApi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Fullstack Playground
  description: Fullstack Playground api docs
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /api/auth/v1/login/email:
    post:
      tags:
        - auth
      summary: Login by Email
      description: Endpoint to login with email and validate it
      requestBody:
        description: Data to do login by email
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              email:
                type: string
            example:
              email: test@test.com
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Email valid
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  companyId:
                    type: string
                  message:
                    type: string
                example:
                  companyId: 9134e286-6f71-427a-bf00-241681624586
                  message: Email successful
        "400":
          description: An error message
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
                  message:
                    type: string
components: {}
tags: []
